description:
This week Anna and Sim sit down with the raddest and the baddest Golden Globe-winning actress, Rachel Bloom (Crazy Ex-Girlfriend)! Anna, Rachel and Sim unpack their experiences clubbing now vs. the past, being teens in summer camp, being married and Rachel tells a story about a shocking social experiment conducted at her summer camp! Finally, Anna and Rachel blueprint their “Golden Girls” inspired retirement plan for 2056- you'll never guess what it is!
